# Components

- `ui/` — generic reusable pieces (buttons, cards, progress)
- `book/` — book reader (slides, cards, headers)
- `lesson/` — lesson player (slides, quiz)
- Themed primitives: `themed-text.tsx`, `themed-view.tsx`
- Colors/typography from `@/constants/theme.ts` — don't hardcode brand colors
- Screen layout wrapper: `tab-screen-layout.tsx`
